    slug: 'countdown-is-on-for-carlisle-skills-fair',
    status: 'publish',
    type: 'post',
    link: 'https://cumbriacrack.com/2024/12/30/countdown-is-on-for-carlisle-skills-fair/',
    title: { rendered: 'Countdown is on for Carlisle Skills Fair' },
    content: {
      rendered:
        '\u003Cdiv class="wp-block-image"\u003E\n\u003Cfigure class="aligncenter size-full"\u003E\u003Cimg loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skills-fair.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-173065" srcset="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skills-fair.jpg 1024w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skills-fair-300x225.jpg 300w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skills-fair-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skills-fair-195x146.jpg 195w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Skills-fair-750x563.jpg 750w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /\u003E\u003Cfigcaption class="wp-element-caption"\u003EJohn Stevenson \u003C/figcaption\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe countdown is on for the next Carlisle Skills Fair. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EHosted by former city MP John Stevenson, the event will take place on Thursday January 23 from 2pm to 6.30pm at Carlisle College.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003ENow in its 11th year, over 80 local employers and education, training and skills providers are set to attend.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003ELast year&#8217;s 10th anniversary skills fair saw a record number of employers and job seekers attending and the 2025 skills fair was looking even better, Mr Stevenson said. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EJohn said: &#8220;The clock striking midnight on New Year&#8217;s Eve often turns thoughts to a fresh start and a time for change in the year ahead.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;For some, this may be the first step on a career path, with a training course or an apprenticeship programme. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;For others, it may be a change of workplace or a change of job and for some it may be the first step to returning to work following a career break.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;I would encourage anyone interested in new opportunities in our local area, to come along on the day and find out more.&#8221;\u003C/p\u003E\n',
      protected: false,
    },
    excerpt: { rendered: '\u003Cp\u003EThe countdown is on for the next Carlisle Skills Fair. \u003C/p\u003E\n', protected: false },
