        '\u003Cdiv class="wp-block-image"\u003E\n\u003Cfigure class="aligncenter size-full"\u003E\u003Cimg loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="556" height="398" src="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Callum-Hewitson-2.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-335700" srcset="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Callum-Hewitson-2.jpg 556w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Callum-Hewitson-2-300x215.jpg 300w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Callum-Hewitson-2-204x146.jpg 204w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Callum-Hewitson-2-350x250.jpg 350w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Callum-Hewitson-2-120x86.jpg 120w" sizes="(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px" /\u003E\u003Cfigcaption class="wp-element-caption"\u003ECallum Hewitson \u003C/figcaption\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAn appeal has been issued for a missing teenager from the Carlisle area.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003ECallum Hewitson, 17, was last seen on December 23.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EHe is described as 6ft, of a slim build, with short, dark brown hair.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EHe may be wearing a dark puffer jacket with a hood, dark tracksuit bottoms and black trainers.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAnyone who has seen Callum is asked to call police on 101.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EIf Callum sees this appeal he is asked to call police on the same number.\u003C/p\u003E\n',
