    slug: 'morrisons-apologises-after-more-card-discounts-glitch',
    status: 'publish',
    type: 'post',
    link: 'https://cumbriacrack.com/2024/12/23/morrisons-apologises-after-more-card-discounts-glitch/',
    title: { rendered: 'Morrisons apologises after More Card discounts glitch' },
    content: {
      rendered:
        '\u003Cdiv class="wp-block-image"\u003E\n\u003Cfigure class="aligncenter size-large"\u003E\u003Cimg loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="684" src="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Morrisons-1024x684.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-63409" srcset="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Morrisons-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Morrisons-300x200.jpg 300w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Morrisons-768x513.jpg 768w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Morrisons-750x501.jpg 750w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Morrisons-1140x761.jpg 1140w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Morrisons.jpg 1204w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003ESupermarket chain Morrisons has apologised after customers have been unable to get shopping discounts due to a problem with the More Card loyalty scheme. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe issues are also impacting Click and Collect orders, the firm said. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EIt said it was experiencing system issues. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThis afternoon, it said had now made the top 100 More Card prices the regular price &#8211; including the 10p veg deal, turkeys, spirits and Champagne. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;And in addition we will give More Card customers an extra 10% off their entire shop today and tomorrow as an apology.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;For More Card customers who have Morrisons Fivers to redeem, these will be done manually in store.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;For Click and Collect orders, we are asking customers to wait for an email to inform them that their order is ready for collection before heading to store. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;Some home delivery orders may be arriving late today &#8211; and we will be communicating directly with those customers affected.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\n\n\u003Cp\u003E&#8220;We sincerely apologise to our customers for this inconvenience.&#8221;\u003C/p\u003E\n',
      protected: false,
    },
    excerpt: {
      rendered:
        '\u003Cp\u003ESupermarket chain Morrisons has apologised after customers have been unable to get shopping discounts due to a problem with the More Card loyalty scheme. \u003C/p\u003E\n',
      protected: false,
    },
