    title: { rendered: 'Afternoon assault in Carlisle street' },
    content: {
      rendered:
        '<div class="wp-block-image">\n<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="681" src="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dagmarbendel-.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-325006" srcset="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dagmarbendel-.jpg 1024w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dagmarbendel--300x200.jpg 300w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dagmarbendel--768x511.jpg 768w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/dagmarbendel--220x146.jpg 220w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Picture: dagmarbendel/Pixabay </figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>A man has been injured thanks to an afternoon assault in a Carlisle street. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Police are investigating the incident, which happened on December 14 at around 2pm in the Hammonds Close area of Upperby in Carlisle.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The victim has sustained injuries to his head and face.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Anyone with information relating to this incident can report online at\u00a0<a href="http://www.cumbria.police.uk/report-it" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">www.cumbria.police.uk/report-it</a>, quoting incident number 122 of the 14 December 2024 or call 101.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, contact Crimestoppers, anonymously, on 0800 555 111.</p>\n',
      protected: false,
    },
