    link: 'https://cumbriacrack.com/2024/12/18/sam-fender-makes-cumbrian-teens-day-at-tebay/',
    title: { rendered: 'Sam Fender makes Cumbrian teen&#8217;s day at Tebay' },
    content: {
      rendered:
        '<div class="wp-block-image">\n<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="860" src="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sam-Fender-.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-334614" srcset="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sam-Fender-.jpg 1024w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sam-Fender--300x252.jpg 300w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sam-Fender--768x645.jpg 768w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sam-Fender--174x146.jpg 174w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Olivia McKinnon and Sam Fender </figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Teenager Olivia McKinnon has an early 18th birthday present when pop star Sam Fender called in at Tebay Services, where she works.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sam, from North Shields, whose hits include Seventeen Going Under, was en route to Glasgow for a concert, which, along with one in Newcastle, was later cancelled due to a vocal chord injury.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Olivia, who lives at Reagill, reported that Sam had the lamb cobbler to eat and a bottle of water.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;He was so friendly and a proper Geordie,&#8221; she said.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Her mum, Michelle, added: &#8220;It\u2019s her 18th birthday on Sunday and she\u2019s a huge fan so it was the perfect birthday surprise for her.&#8221;</p>\n',
      protected: false,
    },
