    modified: '2024-12-18T09:46:23',
    modified_gmt: '2024-12-18T09:46:23',
    slug: 'cumbrias-most-wanted-can-you-help-find-these-people',
    status: 'publish',
    type: 'post',
    link: 'https://cumbriacrack.com/2024/12/18/cumbrias-most-wanted-can-you-help-find-these-people/',
    title: { rendered: 'Cumbria&#8217;s most wanted: Can you help find these people?' },
    content: {
      rendered:
        '<div class="wp-block-image">\n<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="923" height="800" src="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Wanted-4-.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-334541" srcset="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Wanted-4-.jpg 923w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Wanted-4--300x260.jpg 300w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Wanted-4--768x666.jpg 768w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Wanted-4--168x146.jpg 168w" sizes="(max-width: 923px) 100vw, 923px" /></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Four arrests have been made as part of Cumbria police&#8217;s efforts to locate wanted people.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A 42-year-old man, a 37-year-old man and a 19-year-old woman were arrested last weekend and a further arrest was made on Monday December 16, of a 35-year-old woman wanted on recall to prison.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Police said following enquiries, a 28-year-old man is no longer regarded as wanted. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Officers are continuing their appeal for the other individuals who are wanted in connection with ongoing investigations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class="wp-block-list">\n<li><strong>Jonathan Huntley:&nbsp;</strong>The 33-year-old is wanted for breach of court bail. He has links to the Whitehaven area.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Joshua Fawcett:&nbsp;</strong>The 29-year-old is wanted in for wounding. He has links to the Cleator area.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Anthony Moorhead:&nbsp;</strong>The 32-year-old is wanted for malicious communications. He has links to the Carlisle area.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Arron Barbieri:&nbsp;</strong>The 35-year-old is wanted for assault. He has links to the Carlisle area.&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Callum Thompson:&nbsp;</strong>The 38-year-old is wanted for robbery and failing to appear at court. He has links to the Barrow area.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sean Kelly:&nbsp;</strong>The 30-year-old is wanted for aggravated vehicle taking. He has links to the Barrow area.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>John Atkinson:&nbsp;</strong>The 44-year-old is wanted for breach of a supervision order. He has links to the Workington and Barrow areas.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Detective Inspector Dave Howard, of Cumbria Constabulary, said: \u201cWe would like the public\u2019s help in locating the individuals who feature as part of this appeal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cThe appeals are connected to ongoing investigations covering a range of crimes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cEach day, our officers and staff ensure those who are wanted in connection with offences are identified and located so we can progress investigations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cPublic information always will be important in assisting our work to ensure we secure justice for victims.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cPeople in Cumbria know where these individuals are. Please pick up the phone and contact Cumbria police or do so anonymously via Crimestoppers.\u201d&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Anyone with any information regarding the location of these individuals is asked to contact police.<br><br>Report online at&nbsp;<a href="http://www.cumbria.police.uk/report-it">www.cumbria.police.uk/report-it</a>&nbsp;or call 101.<br><br>Alternatively, contact Crimestoppers, anonymously, on 0800 555 111.</p>\n',
      protected: false,
    },
