    title: { rendered: 'New Scout troop in Silloth needs you' },
    content: {
      rendered:
        '<div class="wp-block-image">\n<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/scouts-.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-334447" srcset="https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/scouts-.jpg 1024w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/scouts--300x225.jpg 300w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/scouts--768x576.jpg 768w, https://cumbriacrack.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/scouts--195x146.jpg 195w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Plans are in the pipeline for a new Scout troop to open next year in Silloth.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>1st Silloth Scout Group wants to set up the troop and the team are on the lookout for an adult volunteer to help make it possible.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Scout troop, for children aged 10-and-a-half to 14, will provide opportunities for even more young people in Silloth to have unmissable experiences, make new friends and gain skills for life.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The organisation said whatever people&#8217;s background, identity or ability, there\u2019s a volunteer spot available. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information, email <a href="mailto:Aisha.Ahmed@scouts.org.uk">Aisha.Ahmed@scouts.org.uk</a></p>\n',
      protected: false,
    },
    excerpt: { rendered: '<p>Plans are in the pipeline for a new Scout troop to open next year in Silloth.</p>\n', protected: false },
